Package: minlai
Version: 2.3.8
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Ilshat Minnibaev <ilshatminnibaev@gmail.com>
Depends: python3 (>= 3.11), python3-pip, libxcb-cursor0, libportaudio2
Recommends: flameshot | kde-spectacle, xclip | xsel
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Description: Lightweight system-wide AI assistant for KDE/Linux
 minl.ai is a floating overlay AI assistant powered by Claude or Gemini.
 Trigger it via hotkey to analyze screen regions or selected text.
 Features a system tray icon, settings dialog, light/dark themes, and
 per-session conversation context for follow-up questions.
